lines.text: " That boy ! "That damned fool boy ! What does he mican
by trying to come home now , even if he did promise ?
What aber time mean when weighed against the life of
two human beings ? " Not until he was certain that the
yawl had rounded the rocky point instead of
being flung against the huge boulders did the judge
empty his wings of stifling air and refill them .
with part of that howling northwest gale .
